claim.claim-text:
An apparatus comprising;

means for receiving information from a user equipment comprising at least one packet data protocol context of a target network of a handover procedure and at least one system architecture evolution bearer, wherein said packet data protocol context and system architecture evolution bearer are supported by the user equipment; and

means for mapping, based on the information, in a source network of the handover procedure the at least one supported system architecture evolution bearer to the at least one packet data protocol context.
